<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Oswald' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>FireWater</title>
    <meta name="description" content="What's the minimum shelf price of this liquor?">
    <meta name="author" content="Brian Ryckbost">

    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/1.3.0/bootstrap.min.css" media="screen">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/application.css" media="screen">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.6.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://autobahn.tablesorter.com/jquery.tablesorter.min.js"></script>
    <script>
      $(function() {
        $("table").tablesorter();
      });
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="fill">
        <div class="container">
          <a class="brand" href="#"><span class="fire">Fire</span><span class="water">Water</span></a>
          <ul class="nav">
            <li class="active"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
          <form action="/api/search" class="pull-right">
            <input class="xlarge" type="text" placeholder="Search for Jim Beam, Glenmorangie…">
            <button class="btn" type="submit">Search</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="page-header">
          <h1><span class="fire">Fire</span><span class="water">Water</span> <small>what <strong>should</strong> that bottle of 25 year Laphroaig cost?</small></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="span10">
            <h2>Michigan Liquor Control Commission Price List</h2>
            <table class="zebra-striped">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Brand Name</th>
                  <th>Size (mL)</th>
                  <th>Minimum Shelf Price</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <% @liquors.each do |liquor| %>
                  <tr>
                    <td><%= liquor["BRAND NAME"] %></td>
                    <td><%= liquor["SIZE"] %></td>
                    <td><%= liquor["MINIMUM"] %></td>
                  </tr>
                <% end %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="span4">
            <h3>What's This All About?</h3>
            <p>As of November 30, 2004, liquor license holders may charge a higher price than the state’s set minimum retail selling price.</p>
            <p>However, they may not charge a lower price than the minimum retail shelf price set by the Michigan Liquor Control Commission. <em>Are you getting your money's worth?</em></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <footer>
        <p>&copy; FireWater 2011</p>
      </footer>
    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>
